    • Method Detail

      • toToken

        public Token toToken(InternalSession session)
        Convert from InternalSession to a Token. The InternalSession SessionID instance provides the primary key for the Token. Expiry time is a combination of the InternalSession expiration time and a grace period. Realm is stored in a searchable attribute as it is used by SessionService.getMatchingSessions(Session, CrestQuery) to find all sessions in a given realm. As such this attribute is stored in the realm name format for ease of use.
        Specified by:
        toToken in interface TokenAdapter<InternalSession>
        Parameters:
        session - Non null.
        Returns:
        Non null populated Token.
